{"tid":693920,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"山齊士為摩連奴承諾C朗「7」號球衣感到憤怒","createTime":"2018-06-08T01:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T05:57:58.000Z","uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3ad80f81804c183ca8f6d8321eb4b8f3727092","tid":693920,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T01:26:16.000Z","msg":"Alex Sanchez angry over Mourinho&rsquo;s promise to Ronaldo<br />\n<br />\nSanchez was given the No 7 shirt in January, inheriting the jersey last worn by Memphis Depay.<br />\nMeanwhile, the Red Devils are reportedly edging close to a sensational deal for the Portugal captain, Ronaldo.<br />\n<br />\nNews outlet Don Balon reports that Sanchez is angry after learning Mourinho has promised Ronaldo the No 7 shirt.<br />\n<br />\nThe number is held in high esteem at Old Trafford.<br />\n<br />\nDuring his six years spell at the club, Ronaldo wore the No7 with Sir Alex Ferguson giving it to him despite the Portugal star initially wanting the No 28.<br />\n<br />\nIt is a shirt also made famous by the likes of George Best, Eric Cantona and David Beckham.<br />\n<br />\nSanchez has, however, so far been unable to live up to the hype, managing just three United goals last term.<br />\n<br />\nThe newspaper said Mourinho is ready to give the shirt to the 5-time Balon d&rsquo;Or winner if he returns.<br />\n<br />\nSanchez wanted the number at Barcelona but it was instead worn by Pedro."},{"pid":"564e2f34545e996657d8ca2e83b78df60f47c80a","tid":693920,"uid":39912,"like":13,"dislike":16,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"仆街王咁鳩小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地係世二 你係個回塘老野咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa1e53d3011eae9636151afb74026f5108ee11a","tid":693920,"uid":45772,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T0